Package org.fluentjdbc

Class DatabaseSaveResult<T>

java.lang.Object
org.fluentjdbc.DatabaseSaveResult<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the primary key
public class DatabaseSaveResult<T> extends Object
Encapsulates what operation was executed when data was saved to the database.
  • INSERTED: A row was inserted into the database. getId() contains the generated or specified primary key. getUpdatedFields() is empty
  • UPDATED: A row was updated because fluent-jdbc detected that the data was modified. getUpdatedFields() contains the list of fields that were detected as changed. getId() contains the primary key of the updated row
  • UNCHANGED: Nothing was updated as fluent-jdbc determined that the values in the database were equal to the specified values. getId() contains the primary key of the row used for comparison
  • DELETED: The row was deleted. Only supported by DbContextSyncBuilder
